\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "galvani2016,Ferreira2019"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
 Furthermore, one of the key features is the possibility of engineering
 the effect of interactions by changing the substrate.
 Introducing a substrate with a higher dielectric constant effectively screens
 electronic interactions, thereby reducing the energy required to bind the
